[QB]&gt;&gt;and both of these components operate independantly.

I wouldn't be too sure of that.  The Necro DoT ones do operate independently.  That's because their system doesn't let them link an effect on a player with an effect on a mob.  With the nukes though, that isn't necessarily the case.  A critical blast on the garou proc raises the healing portion as well.  That would seem to indicate that the garou damage has a direct impact upon how much you heal.  Now, there could be special code in there that says to raise both on a critical blast, but it could also be that they are tied together.[/QB][/QUOTE]
