<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">
Beyond a certain level, NPCs start giving you less mana when you use Theft of Thought, I think the level is around 52 or 53.  It just happens that the casters in Ssraeshza are above that level.. you can notice it in other zones too, using Theft of Thought on an ilis or reet wizard in Sebilis gives you the smaller mana amount compared to a krup wizard.<P>Valdayana D'Varr (Quellious server)
